{"tid":2235322,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"港男脫毒必學! 24種韓國小鮮肉最常見既秋冬穿搭造型","createTime":"2020-10-08T14:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T08:34:07.000Z","uid":353419,"like":2,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"eca1cced40b697db05fd7a8b3f6eb92912240334","tid":2235322,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T14:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hlXhAB1MVM3dVOBiei8xMIG9uMBhmVCB0MQ5iaApWbUMtASB0aw5-GXY8PRVwD3QpPF9-EHQ8KEYoWiR2OVZ-/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hlXhAB1MVM3dVOBiei8xMIG9uMBhmVCB0MQ5iaApWbUMtASB0aw5-GXY8PRVwD3QpPF9-EHQ8KEYoWiR2OVZ-%2Fw1200&h=74b37f98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朴寶劍的清新氣度<br />\n韓式西裝與普通西裝的分別是前者剪裁富時代感，最明顯的分別在於那非過分修身的西裝外套及吊腳款式，這兩項都是決定性的細節，就像朴寶劍這身造型一樣；而另外一雙白色皮革 loafers 亦有提亮造型的效果！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hElG0rjjkGkN6STGqpLJlFEAfGSxJJQlAHn9LXCUnRHcCcAlARH8HLVlMQiNReV0dEy5XJlhPAXIHKw1CFicH/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hElG0rjjkGkN6STGqpLJlFEAfGSxJJQlAHn9LXCUnRHcCcAlARH8HLVlMQiNReV0dEy5XJlhPAXIHKw1CFicH%2Fw1200&h=ec77dbdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杏色西裝套裝的重點落在孖襟款式之上，感覺比普通西裝褸更加年輕。特別欣賞朴寶劍以黑白間紋作這淺色西裝的配搭，將清新和秀氣全面注入造型之中。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hkxEMrRBaNFd4NB--psVLAEJiNzhLWCdUHAJlSCdaamMADSdURgJ8OVswOmJVAHMJFlp7M1s0L2YFViNWFFp8/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hkxEMrRBaNFd4NB--psVLAEJiNzhLWCdUHAJlSCdaamMADSdURgJ8OVswOmJVAHMJFlp7M1s0L2YFViNWFFp8%2Fw1200&h=fdfd3a75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一件套頭上衣是秋日最方面百搭的單品之一，不管是衛衣或是像朴寶劍這種圖案冷衫，襯上簡單的黑色九分直腳褲和波鞋已經十分耐看！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0h66s2ZAbJaRlOS0LwkLcWTnQdanZ9J3oaKn04BhElNy02cnoacH11d20ZYCBmeS5HJywkfG9DcigzKX4YIiV1/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0h66s2ZAbJaRlOS0LwkLcWTnQdanZ9J3oaKn04BhElNy02cnoacH11d20ZYCBmeS5HJywkfG9DcigzKX4YIiV1%2Fw1200&h=78f233be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n穿上 Thom Browne 西裝套裝的朴寶劍零舍討人喜愛，尤其是那 iconic 的間紋細節，感覺就像英國王室般的貴族一樣矜貴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0htVyjoCdjK3lEEwCQmu5ULn5FKBZ3fzh6ICV6Zht9dU08Kjh6eiU0F2cQchw8K2wnKn1kGmQWMEg5cTx4KH00/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0htVyjoCdjK3lEEwCQmu5ULn5FKBZ3fzh6ICV6Zht9dU08Kjh6eiU0F2cQchw8K2wnKn1kGmQWMEg5cTx4KH00%2Fw1200&h=be950067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車銀優的年輕混搭<br />\n粉藍色 Oxford shirt 有種令人變帥的魔力，學似新晉韓國鮮肉車銀優般以印有紋理的短款西裝褸作配搭，年輕之中滲透幾分正經氣質。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hZUTTxeTlBXppLS6Tt8p6LVN7BhVaQRZ5DRtUZTZDW04RFBZ5VxhLFEolWkhNTkIkB0NKGEklHksUTxJ7BRtL/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hZUTTxeTlBXppLS6Tt8p6LVN7BhVaQRZ5DRtUZTZDW04RFBZ5VxhLFEolWkhNTkIkB0NKGEklHksUTxJ7BRtL%2Fw1200&h=0a9bed8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n的確！西褲襯涼鞋可能會給人「落街」之感，但大家卻可以靠衣飾單品去提高時尚指數，就像車銀優這身打扮，以流行的開胸夏威夷圖案恤衫與皮 clutch 作造型調味，把涼鞋的隨性演變成帶有層次感的風格，最適合初秋的假日不過！<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hHZMeRKz9F3VwHDycrvtoIkpKFBpDcAR2FCpGai9ySUEIJQR2TilZG1MbQEYJJFArHnJYF1AbDEQNfgB0HCpZ/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hHZMeRKz9F3VwHDycrvtoIkpKFBpDcAR2FCpGai9ySUEIJQR2TilZG1MbQEYJJFArHnJYF1AbDEQNfgB0HCpZ%2Fw1200&h=e8aeff53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條紋西裝可以老套也可以非常時髦，重點是紋條圖案的分佈與西裝底色的挑選，緊記盡量避免深藍、深紅等過份成熟的用色，而紋條設計亦可以利用流行的白車線（line stitching）作代替，就好像車銀優這身西裝套裝一般，顯得特別年輕及清新。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hx4hvv9CEJxtVDwzyi-lYTG9ZJHRmYzQYMTl2BApheS8tNjQYazpodXYKcHgrbWBFO2FoeXYMPCoobTAaOTlo/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hx4hvv9CEJxtVDwzyi-lYTG9ZJHRmYzQYMTl2BApheS8tNjQYazpodXYKcHgrbWBFO2FoeXYMPCoobTAaOTlo%2Fw1200&h=6c8adc1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019 年的秋冬男士穿搭仍然流行各式各樣的 bomber jacket，車銀優就選擇了薄身的短夾克襯貼身西褲和 Converse 布鞋，簡單炮製出韓星般的機場穿搭 style。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hbytUZtzlPVZJLBa_l9RCAXN6Pjl6QC5VLRpsSRZCY2IxFS5VdxolOGokYW83GXoIIEtwMmguJmc0TipXJUIl/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hbytUZtzlPVZJLBa_l9RCAXN6Pjl6QC5VLRpsSRZCY2IxFS5VdxolOGokYW83GXoIIEtwMmguJmc0TipXJUIl%2Fw1200&h=d8146b56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朴敘俊的簡約成熟<br />\n朴敘俊以超短髮襯薄身開胸恤衫和西褲，打造出成熟而 effortless 的氣質；加上經典的全白波鞋和鋼帶手錶，表面簡單的造型但實際隱藏不同的細節去營造富質感的形象。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hPaArFLPoD058CySnovlwGUZdDCFPZxxNGD1eUSNlUXoEMhxNQj1EIF9ZAy5ZbEgQEmVAKl4NFH8BaRhPEGVE/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hPaArFLPoD058CySnovlwGUZdDCFPZxxNGD1eUSNlUXoEMhxNQj1EIF9ZAy5ZbEgQEmVAKl4NFH8BaRhPEGVE%2Fw1200&h=8d9c1d10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n別看輕一件極 plain 的針織套頭衫，其實它是男版韓式秋冬穿搭的其中一個精髓！可以選擇朴敘俊這類暗粉色系，但若然閣下嫌粉紅粉藍太過嬌情，冷不防一件素色設計如灰色或 navy blue 同樣擁有 decent 的效果，下身襯上一條壓骨西褲經已夠好看。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hm3VviTp4MhxrDxn1tf9NS1FZMXNYYyEfDzljAzRhbCgTNiEfVTl7ckgIPi9GNnVCBWF9eEcLKS0WbSUdB2F7/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hm3VviTp4MhxrDxn1tf9NS1FZMXNYYyEfDzljAzRhbCgTNiEfVTl7ckgIPi9GNnVCBWF9eEcLKS0WbSUdB2F7%2Fw1200&h=fb36e758&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0h2LdigT8zbWNZEEaKh-oSNGNGbgxqfH5gPSY8fAZ-M1chKX5gZyZ3DXoYNgB9KCo9MHcgBnQSdlIkcnpiNX53/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0h2LdigT8zbWNZEEaKh-oSNGNGbgxqfH5gPSY8fAZ-M1chKX5gZyZ3DXoYNgB9KCo9MHcgBnQSdlIkcnpiNX53%2Fw1200&h=48240b9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hD4JbR1-FGxt3GzDyqeZkTE1NGHREdwgYEy1KBCh1RS8PIggYSS0EdVQdFnhdKlxFGXVUeFASACoKeQwaG3UE/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hD4JbR1-FGxt3GzDyqeZkTE1NGHREdwgYEy1KBCh1RS8PIggYSS0EdVQdFnhdKlxFGXVUeFASACoKeQwaG3UE%2Fw1200&h=0cbeb7e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0h9TDWwwARZnt5Lk2Sp8kZLEN4ZRRKQnV4HRg3ZCZAOE8BF3V4RxsoFVp7O04EFyElF0ApGVksfUoETHF6FRgo/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0h9TDWwwARZnt5Lk2Sp8kZLEN4ZRRKQnV4HRg3ZCZAOE8BF3V4RxsoFVp7O04EFyElF0ApGVksfUoETHF6FRgo%2Fw1200&h=614a2a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hNASfIGCyEW5uHzqHsO9uOVRJEgFdcwJtCilAcTFxT1oWJgJtUClYAE0aH10TJlYwAHFeCkIfCl8TfQZvAnFY/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hNASfIGCyEW5uHzqHsO9uOVRJEgFdcwJtCilAcTFxT1oWJgJtUClYAE0aH10TJlYwAHFeCkIfCl8TfQZvAnFY%2Fw1200&h=30bb2bf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hqEpJRFtSLmpNMwWDk85RPXdlLQV-Xz1pKQV_dRJdcF41Cj1pcwUxBG41IwoyA2k0I11hCW06NVswUTlrIV0x/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hqEpJRFtSLmpNMwWDk85RPXdlLQV-Xz1pKQV_dRJdcF41Cj1pcwUxBG41IwoyA2k0I11hCW06NVswUTlrIV0x%2Fw1200&h=e93492c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hg7OXLW4hOBhyIRPxrNpHT0h3O3dBTSsbFhdpBy1PZiwKGCsbTBcldlEiYS5dQX9GG0Z1fVEgIykPQy8ZHk8l/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hg7OXLW4hOBhyIRPxrNpHT0h3O3dBTSsbFhdpBy1PZiwKGCsbTBcldlEiYS5dQX9GG0Z1fVEgIykPQy8ZHk8l%2Fw1200&h=5df47d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hIP2FTXlxFn8PPz2W0cFpKDVpFRA8UwV8awlHYFBRSEt3BgV8MQlRESw8HBh1CFEhYVFZGyI3DU5yXQF-Y1FR/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hIP2FTXlxFn8PPz2W0cFpKDVpFRA8UwV8awlHYFBRSEt3BgV8MQlRESw8HBh1CFEhYVFZGyI3DU5yXQF-Y1FR%2Fw1200&h=8bbae40e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hpUKp4y1KL3p2CQSTqPhQLUxfLBVFZTx5Ej9-ZSlncU4OMDx5SD9nFFULck1cOWgkGGdgHlUANEsLazh7Gmdn/w1200\" data-thumb